msgid ""
"Hi ###USERNAME###,\n"
"\n"
"This notice confirms that your email address on ###SITENAME### was changed to ###NEW_EMAIL###.\n"
"\n"
"If you did not change your email, please contact the Site Administrator at\n"
"###ADMIN_EMAIL###\n"
